[SN]TITLE[SN]
Robots that recycle your old TV

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
As TV technology advances, we are upgrading more often - and in the UK two million sets are thrown away each year with many ending up in landfill.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
11 November 2016 Last updated at 00:46 GMT
Discarded electrical goods are the fastest growing form of waste, with TVs making up the biggest element - and that's a huge headache for councils that have to deal with it.
